Raise Dead

Active
Necromancer Start

4 Mana

Create a zombie on your side.
Whenever it takes damage, you take 10% of that damage as Neuro. This does not reduce the damage the zombie takes.
Its stats are a fraction of yours:

80% Strength
90% Toughness
40% Agility
20% Intuition
20% Intellect
20% Will

